The paper discusses the accuracy of confidence intervals for field-normalized indicators, which is a topic that could fall under several arXiv CS sub-categories. However, based on the content of the abstract, the most likely sub-category is cs.CY (Computational Geometry), as the paper appears to be focused on statistical analysis and simulation. Other possible sub-categories include cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
